```
#ifdef DEBUG
    /* Give the function a unique number */

    if (opts.disAsm || opts.dspEmit || verbose)
    {
        compMethodNumber = ~info.compMethodHash() & 0xffff;
    }
    else
    {
        compMethodNumber = s_compMethodsCount;
        s_compMethodsCount++;
    }
#endif
```
And the calls to:
